propose_moves.prompt:
Your name is agent_1. You are in an environment with the following public information:
{environment->public_information}
You have the following private knowledge:
{agents->agent_1->private_information}
Your task:
Produce an ordered list of primitive moves (one move per line) in the format 'agent_1: move disk X from peg1 to peg2'. Moves must respect Tower of Hanoi rules and you may only move the disks you are allowed to. Assume the other agent will propose complementary moves for the disks they can move. Do not provide PDDL; only provide the move list.

